<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ title }} – Handout-Draft</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/fonts/fonts.css">
  <style>
    :root{
      --navy:#1c2b3a;
      --teal:#1e656d;
      --teal-soft:#d9ecec;
      --warm:#fcf8f4;
      --sand:#ddd2bf;
      --alert:#9a3412;
      --text:#2d2823;
      --muted:#5c5a56;
      --line:rgba(45,40,35,0.12);
      --paper:#fffdf9;
      --shadow:0 18px 42px rgba(28,43,58,0.12);
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{background:#efe8df}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(141,212,217,0.16), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f4eee6 0%, #ece3d9 100%);
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    a{color:var(--teal)}

    .draft-shell{
      width:min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin:32px auto 48px;
    }

    .draft-toolbar{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:flex-start;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .draft-intro{
      max-width:56ch;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    .draft-actions{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .draft-chip,
    .draft-link{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      min-height:40px;
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-size:0.82rem;
      font-weight:700;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      color:var(--navy);
      backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
    }

    .draft-link.primary{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),var(--teal));
      color:#fff;
      border-color:transparent;
    }

    .draft-paper{
      width:210mm;
      min-height:297mm;
      margin:0 auto;
      background:var(--paper);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      border:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
    }

    .draft-header{
      padding:22mm 18mm 10mm;
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(141,212,217,0.18), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(252,248,244,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.92));
    }

    .draft-kicker{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      align-items:center;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }

    .draft-badge{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:5px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:var(--teal-soft);
      color:var(--navy);
      font-size:0.68rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:0.08em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .draft-badge.alert{background:#f6ddd5;color:var(--alert)}
    .draft-title{
      font-family:'Source Serif 4',serif;
      font-size:2rem;
      line-height:1.12;
      letter-spacing:-0.02em;
      margin:0 0 10px;
      color:var(--navy);
    }

    .draft-subtitle{
      font-size:1rem;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:58ch;
      margin:0 0 14px;
    }

    .draft-meta{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));
      gap:10px;
    }

    .draft-meta-card{
      border:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:12px 14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    }

    .draft-meta-label{
      font-size:0.68rem;
      font-weight:700;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:0.08em;
      color:#6f6b65;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .draft-meta-value{
      font-size:0.85rem;
      color:var(--text);
      font-weight:600;
    }

    .draft-content{
      padding:14mm 18mm 18mm;
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    .draft-content > :first-child{margin-top:0}
    .draft-content h1{display:none}
    .draft-content h2{
      font-family:'Source Serif 4',serif;
      font-size:1.28rem;
      line-height:1.2;
      color:var(--navy);
      margin:1.8rem 0 0.7rem;
      padding-bottom:0.25rem;
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    }

    .draft-content h3{
      font-size:1rem;
      line-height:1.35;
      color:var(--navy);
      margin:1.15rem 0 0.45rem;
    }

    .draft-content p{margin:0.55rem 0}
    .draft-content ul{margin:0.55rem 0 0.8rem 1.15rem;padding:0}
    .draft-content li{margin:0.2rem 0}
    .draft-content strong{color:var(--navy)}
    .draft-content code{
      background:#f2eee8;
      border-radius:6px;
      padding:1px 6px;
      font-size:0.9em;
    }

    .draft-footer{
      margin-top:auto;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
      padding:10mm 18mm 14mm;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      color:#6f6b65;
      font-size:0.78rem;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.92), rgba(252,248,244,0.95));
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px){
      .draft-shell{width:min(100%, calc(100% - 20px));margin:18px auto 28px}
      .draft-paper{width:100%;min-height:auto}
      .draft-header,.draft-content,.draft-footer{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
      .draft-header{padding-top:22px}
      .draft-content{padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:24px}
      .draft-footer{padding-top:18px}
      .draft-meta{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .draft-title{font-size:1.7rem}
    }

    @media print{
      html,body{background:#fff}
      .draft-shell{width:auto;margin:0}
      .draft-toolbar{display:none}
      .draft-paper{
        width:auto;
        min-height:auto;
        margin:0;
        box-shadow:none;
        border:none;
      }
      .draft-header,.draft-content,.draft-footer{
        padding-left:14mm;
        padding-right:14mm;
      }
      .draft-header{padding-top:14mm}
      .draft-content{padding-top:10mm;padding-bottom:12mm}
      .draft-footer{padding-top:8mm;padding-bottom:10mm}
      a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="draft-shell">
    <div class="draft-toolbar">
      <div class="draft-intro">
        Dies ist eine wartbare HTML-Voransicht für den Neuaufbau eines Handouts. Sie dient als Zwischenstufe für redaktionelle Prüfung, Layout-Feinschliff und späteren PDF-Export.
      </div>
      <div class="draft-actions">
        <span class="draft-chip">{{ type }}</span>
        <span class="draft-chip">{{ target_format }}</span>
        {% if source_pdf %}<a class="draft-link" href="{{ source_pdf }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Altes PDF öffnen</a>{% endif %}
        <a class="draft-link primary" href="/handout-drafts/">Alle Drafts</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <article class="draft-paper">
      <header class="draft-header">
        <div class="draft-kicker">
          <span class="draft-badge">{{ priority }}</span>
          <span class="draft-badge{% if type == 'Akutblatt' %} alert{% endif %}">{{ type }}</span>
          <span class="draft-badge">{{ status }}</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="draft-title">{{ title }}</h1>
        <p class="draft-subtitle">{{ goal }}</p>
        <div class="draft-meta">
          <div class="draft-meta-card">
            <div class="draft-meta-label">Zielgruppe</div>
            <div class="draft-meta-value">{{ audience }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="draft-meta-card">
            <div class="draft-meta-label">Quell-PDF</div>
            <div class="draft-meta-value">{{ source_pdf }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="draft-meta-card">
            <div class="draft-meta-label">Stand</div>
            <div class="draft-meta-value">{{ last_updated }}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="draft-content">
        {{ content | safe }}
      </main>

      <footer class="draft-footer">
        <div>PUK Zürich · Handout-Draft-System</div>
        <div>{{ slug }} · noch nicht final exportiert</div>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
